						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone built into the front wall of the village gate.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription written in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">12th century A.D.,</hi> records the death of a hero (name lost), while fighting with <hi rend="bold">Siṁgaṇa-Dāṇḍānāyaka,</hi> the <hi rend="italic">adhikāri</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Hāvri.</hi> Some grant seṇems to have been made in his memory. A certain <hi rend="bold">Mchidēvaē</hi> is mentioned.</p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
